Question No: 4

Write a Java program that connects to a database using JDBC, 
and retrieves metadata about the columns in a given table

Table:customer_details

Use the below Database Credentials
Driver Class        :           com.mysql.jdbc.Driver
Default DB URL :            jdbc:mysql://localhost/ri_db
Username          :            test
Password           :            test123


Input format
No console input

Output format
The Output Should display the ColumnName and datatype of the Column of customer_details Table


Sample testcases
Input 1						    Output 1
						          ColumnName  TypeOfColumn
						          cust_ID (INT) 10
						          cust_Name (VARCHAR) 100
						          city (VARCHAR) 100
